metadata.name: STRINGS PROTOTYPE :::..._ #1/2
metadata.description:
[STRINGS :::...I ••°|...] process work, bidders edition of 20 

 “I've been obsessed with this for a while... I started with math symbols such as  :::...I ••°|...”

My journey has been filled with people who extended their hand to help me reach out great opportunities and progress in my art career. Back in 2020, one of those kind gestures allowed me to have a proper computer which changed not only the quality of my outputs but my will to create a t higher speed and rate. because I had the necessary tools to keep evolving. Today “Fund the Jump” emulates this good deed by providing many young artists with the support to make a real change in their lives and create a string of positive effects in the future of technology.
